00:00:41.860 --> 00:00:43.600
And the first thing
before we start,

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:48.380
I'm going to
discuss how I write,

00:00:48.380 --> 00:00:52.040
how the whole body
of work is organized,

00:00:52.040 --> 00:00:56.340
