00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:11.720
So a book cannot be about an
idea no more than a painting is

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.280
about something other
than being a painting.

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:17.630
So a book has to be
self-standing item that you

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:19.620
cannot reduce.

00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:22.440
And that may communicate
some message or not,

00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:23.690
that's not the relevant point.

00:01:23.690 --> 00:01:26.050
It [? cannot ?] be organized
in a way that you read it

00:01:26.050 --> 00:01:27.860
in fractal way.

00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:33.520
So the way it's written, you
have sentences, paragraphs,

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:36.970
sections, chapters, and volumes.

00:01:36.970 --> 00:01:39.010
And everything has to be
integrated as a whole.

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:42.100
So that's the idea
of the "Incerto,"

00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:46.420
five volumes on uncertainty.

00:01:46.420 --> 00:01:53.080
And the idea is, for
the author to write

00:01:53.080 --> 00:01:54.700
on his or her own terms.

00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:56.780
That's my idea how an
author should write.

00:01:56.780 --> 00:01:59.650
And I do it myself
with passion, all

00:01:59.650 --> 00:02:01.460
right, I write on my own terms.

00:02:01.460 --> 00:02:04.930
