So what is my modus operandi
while writing the "Incerto?"

00:02:48.395 --> 00:02:52.180
Now, there is a
restaurant called--

00:02:52.180 --> 00:02:54.970
used to be a restaurant called
Lindy that closed on the day

00:02:54.970 --> 00:02:56.310
this was published.

